      "blocks": {
        "question_GEKcy4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What’s included in Heybike 4th Anniversary Celebration?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>We're celebrating 4 amazing years with unbeatable deals and exciting gifts! Here's what you can enjoy:</p><ul><li><strong>Best Deals Ever</strong> on All Ebikes</li><li><strong>Extra $100 Coupon</strong> with code \"ANNIVERSARY\"</li><li><strong>Free Baskets</strong> with select models</li><li><strong>60-Day Price Match Guarantee</strong></li><li><strong>Green Rides Campaign With </strong><em><strong>OneTreePlanted</strong></em></li></ul><p>Even more anniversary giveaways & surprises await! Stay in the loop—<a href=\"https://www.heybike.com/account/register\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.heybike.com/account/register\"><em><strong>subscribe</strong></em></a> to our emails for exclusive offers and the latest event updates!</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_tncXgJ": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What is the 60-Day Price Match Guarantee?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>We guarantee price protection for orders placed during Heybike 4th Anniversary Sale. If you find a lower price on the exact same product within 60 days of your purchase on Heybike official website, simply reach out to our customer service team with proof of the lower price. Our team will verify the information, and issue a refund for the price difference depending on the specific situation.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_b4HpKq": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>When can I expect my ebike order to ship?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Generally each ebike order will be shipped within 1-2 businss days.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
